trans-unit.source: Represents an entry in either back or forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en post i tillbaka eller vidarebefordra historik.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] implements a navigation history service that stores one entry for each piece of content that has been previously navigated to, just like navigation history in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)]implementerar en navigering historik tjänst som lagrar en post för varje typ av innehåll som tidigare har varit efter att, precis som historik i [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Navigation history comprises two stacks, one that remembers back navigation history, and one that remembers forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Historik består av två grupper, en som kommer ihåg tillbaka historik och en som kommer ihåg navigering framåt historik.

trans-unit.source: An entry for the current item is added to back navigation history when a forward navigation occurs.
trans-unit.target: En post för det aktuella objektet har lagts till igen historik när en vanlig navigation inträffar.

trans-unit.source: This occurs in the following situations: - The `Navigate` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: Detta inträffar i följande situationer: – `Navigate` metoden anropas (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The `GoForward` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: - `GoForward` Metoden anropas (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The forward button on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that is displayed from the current navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: -Knappen vidarebefordra i navigeringen till [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] som visas i den aktuella Navigatören ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Likewise, an entry for the current item is added to forward navigation history before a back navigation occurs, which happens when: - The `GoBack` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: På samma sätt kan en post för det aktuella objektet har lagts till navigering framåt historik innan en bakre navigation inträffar, som händer när: – `GoBack` metoden anropas (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The back button on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that is displayed from the current navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: -Bakåt-knappen i navigeringen till [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] som visas i den aktuella Navigatören ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Each entry in back and forward navigation history is an instance of the JournalEntry class.
trans-unit.target: Varje post i tillbaka och navigering framåt historik är en instans av klassen JournalEntry.

trans-unit.source: Each JournalEntry object encapsulates information about a particular navigation, including a name for the entry (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>), whether the entry is kept alive (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A>) and the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for the content that is navigated to (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Varje JournalEntry-objekt innehåller information om en viss navigering, inklusive ett namn för posten (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>), oavsett om posten sparas alive (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A>) och [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] för det innehåll som har navigerat till (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can retrieve all the JournalEntry objects in back navigation history by enumerating the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties.
trans-unit.target: Du kan hämta alla JournalEntry objekt i den bakre historik genom uppräkning av <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For forward navigation history, you can retrieve all the JournalEntry objects by enumerating the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties.
trans-unit.target: För navigering framåt tidigare, kan du hämta alla JournalEntry objekt genom uppräkning av <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If you need to remove the most recent JournalEntry object from back navigation history, to prevent navigation to it, for example, you can call the `RemoveBackEntry` method (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), which removes the JournalEntry object and returns a reference to it.
trans-unit.target: Om du behöver ta bort det senaste JournalEntry-objektet från tillbaka historik för att förhindra att navigering till den, till exempel kan du anropa den `RemoveBackEntry` metod (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), som tar bort JournalEntry-objektet och returnerar en referens till den.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You cannot add JournalEntry objects to navigation history, however, because you can neither instantiate nor derive from JournalEntry, and because no type implements a member to do so.
trans-unit.target: Du kan inte lägga till JournalEntry objekt historik, men eftersom du kan varken instansiera eller härledd från JournalEntry, och inga typen implementerar en medlem för att göra det.

trans-unit.source: However, you can add custom <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> objects to back navigation history by calling the `AddBackEntry` method (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A>); <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> adds the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object to an internally-created JournalEntry object, which is then added to the back navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Du kan dock lägga till anpassade <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>objekt om du vill säkerhetskopiera historik genom att anropa den `AddBackEntry` metod (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A>); <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>lägger till den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>objekt till ett internt skapade JournalEntry objekt, som sedan läggs till i navigering bakåt tidigare.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>
